'''Togorian''' was the native language of the [[Togorian/Legends|Togorian]] [[Species/Legends|species]] from [[Togoria/Legends|Togoria]]. It was a harsh-sounding language.<ref name="UAA">''[[Ultimate Alien Anthology]]''</ref>

Most Togorians were fluent in both Togorian language and [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]], although they were only literate in their own language.<ref name="UAA" />

